  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aortic valve area &lt; 1cm2

          -  Indexed aortic valve area &lt;0.6 cm/m2

          -  Maximum Jet velocity &gt; 4.0 m/sec

          -  Mean transvalvular gradient &gt; 40 mmHg

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Non-severe aortic Stenosis (AS)

          -  Previous aortic valve replacement (AVR)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
